Class LongRunningRecognizeMetadata.Builder (2.0.0)

public static final class LongRunningRecognizeMetadata.Builder extends GeneratedMessageV3.Builder<LongRunningRecognizeMetadata.Builder> implements LongRunningRecognizeMetadataOrBuilder

Describes the progress of a long-running LongRunningRecognize call. It is included in the metadata field of the Operation returned by the GetOperation call of the google::longrunning::Operations service.
